    <item>
      <title>高盛、摩根士丹利正在为风险最高的抵押贷款债券提供支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/goldman-morgan-stanley-are-backstopping-riskiest-slices-of-clos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团和摩根士丹利越来越愿意暂时持有新抵押贷款债务中风险最高的部分，以期在帮助企业将杠杆贷款打包成债券这一再次蓬勃发展的业务中赢得更多市场份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/goldman-morgan-stanley-are-backstopping-riskiest-slices-of-clos</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 12:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
